data.description: Welcome to Cherrywood an Active Adult community in SW Ocala.  This spacious home offers cathedral ceillings, split bedroom plan, living room, dining and family room. The park-like setting offered in the backyard makes this a great location to enjoy through many windows and enclosed lanai. The oversized master suite offers two walk in closets and and a bright master bath with separate garden tub and shower. Also, enjoy the  separation of dual sinks and vanity area. The living room and family room offer plenty of livability, especially for the piano! The kitchen is loaded with counter space and cabinets galore offering great storage plus a closet pantry.  The additional 2 bedrooms can be used as office or bedrooms. Enjoy the screen enclosed lanai overlooking a parklike setting in the backyard. Fenced backyard. Indoor laundry room.  The home offers a spacious 2 car garage.  Cherrywood clubhouse features a fitness center, hobby rooms, pool and activities for the homeowners. Spectrum basic cable tv, and trash pickup are included in the monthly fees.  New roof and HVAC make this a great home for the next homeowner.
